{"tid":913353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星折疊式手機Galaxy Flex售價不斐　傳起價可能近2,000美元","createTime":"2018-11-23T10:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T15:00:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c782f3c52920202116c0a73d225135d8d3145072","tid":913353,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"三星電子(Samsung Electronics)Galaxy Flex螢幕折疊手機呼之欲出，一般認為由於手機軟硬體使用尖端技術，售價可能不斐，果然有爆料者透露，Flex起價接近2,000美元。<br />\n <br />\nGizmodo引述三星內部員工消息指出，Galaxy Flex價格介於1,500英鎊(約1,921美元)至2,000英鎊，由價格區間推測，Galaxy Flex顯然有多種版本。在英國，消費者僅能在三星線上商店和電信商EE購買。<br />\n <br />\n三星對此消息發表一份聲明表示，折疊式手機訂於2019年上半在特定市場推出，現在已準備量產，預估產量至少為100萬支。<br />\n <br />\n智慧型手機售價最近才正式突破1,000美元，如此高貴的價格讓一般消費者卻步，GalaxyFlex卻要價近2,000美元，預料多數消費者也難以接受。<br />\n <br />\n不過，三星目前提供購買手機不綁約(SIM-free)方案「Samsung Upgrade Program」，消費者只要付10%的頭期款，餘額分兩年分攤償還，滿12個月就可升級換購新手機，GalaxyFlex是否包含在此方案內目前不得而知，若能分期付款可能有助於吸引消費者。"},{"pid":"54bece7e0fd0ce268c0c5afb03654ab0ed4a83a0","tid":913353,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90785f027cac4c80b7202de9312750389f8b1bee","tid":913353,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"就快買電話都要儲首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f42c2960026eddccf024ed462d3dae6451acda","tid":913353,"uid":170438,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"當正自己名牌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ce5e98420ea1117347d9f0a54608885d2e40ff","tid":913353,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e19c7226e5041d16e674aa34737c0b7e7d5ffdd","tid":913353,"uid":22337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"200美金可以諗諗"},{"pid":"85b032620f1eb7821892485da65c9d1a6d0cd229","tid":913353,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"1萬4咋 iPhone X's max 都要萬1啦"}]}